_sText:
Maximun Players = 44  (22 CT, 22 T)

A Japanese house styled map where you surf from roof top to roof top.  There are sniping perches, secret rooms, and secret buttons.  Enjoy simple surf, easy surf.  For those of you who want something harder, try pulling out some tricks, there are some pretty cool tricks you can do on this map.  For another good "trick" map, try my  "surf_greatriver"  .  In japan_v3, expect to find:   
A Jail
More buttons
More rooms
More Houses
and much more fun!!

Tester:  B~A~Baracus
